/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/CHAIN-HISTORY.md:1498:This route still mines genuinely exact Navier-Stokes structure not captured by the averaged comparison model, but it no longer treats representational novelty as progress. A stochastic observable is promoted only if it touches a specific singularity mechanism under honest localization, solution-class pressure, and theorem-facing insertion.
